				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5980008#post-3807981</guid>
				<title>Poober</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5980008/scp-3494#post-3807981</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Mon, 21 May 2018 21:45:15 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Ensophos</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1676981</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>This is the best insight you've given us into the mindset of Dado yet. Boner Pill was good solely in its take on the sophomorically anomalous erection, which didn't do it for me (lol don't read into that); Banana Dose was good in outlining the logical fallacies that guide his work. This took it to a philosophical level; this peeled back the strictly-business front of Dado with the hint he might dream of an outsourced poo-topia. And then he presented it with such honest, unflinching conviction that I found myself shaking my head. It was brief, but it happened.</p> <p>That was, of course, the moment I upvoted this article.<br /> I've begun to trust in Dado.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
